# 접근성 하이라이트 오버레이 {#accessibility-highlight-overlay}

`Dali::Ui::AccessibilityHighlightOverlay` lets a dali-ui app manage the visible accessibility highlight overlay 위해 the 현재 highlight actor.

## 목차 {#table-of-contents}

- [생성할 항목: an Overlay Controller.](#create-an-overlay-controller)
- [사용할 항목: Automatic Highlight Placement.](#use-automatic-highlight-placement)
- [사용할 항목: a 사용자 지정 Highlight Rectangle.](#use-a-custom-highlight-rectangle)
- [Reset 또는 Hide the Overlay.](#reset-or-hide-the-overlay)
- [Query 및 Preserve Overlay Mode.](#query-and-preserve-overlay-mode)

## 생성 an Overlay Controller {#create-an-overlay-controller}

생성할 항목: one `Dali::Ui::AccessibilityHighlightOverlay` 위해 the part의 your dali-ui app that coordinates accessibility highlight rendering. 해당 객체 저장합니다 the 현재 `Dali::Ui::OverlayHighlightMode` 및 the manual rectangle configured through `SetCustomHighlight`.

```cpp
#include <dali-ui-foundation/integration-api/accessibility-highlight-overlay.h>

class AccessibilityOverlayController
{
public:
  AccessibilityOverlayController()
  : mHighlightOverlay()
  {
  }

private:
  Dali::Ui::AccessibilityHighlightOverlay mHighlightOverlay;
};
```

유지할 항목: your app UI structured around `Dali::Ui::View` 객체. 해당 overlay controller는 companion 객체: it does not replace your 뷰, 및 it does not require 애플리케이션 code에 configure the overlay actors directly.

```cpp
#include <dali-ui-foundation/integration-api/accessibility-highlight-overlay.h>

class AccessiblePanel
{
public:
  AccessiblePanel()
  : mHighlightOverlay()
  {
  }

  Dali::Ui::AccessibilityHighlightOverlay& GetHighlightOverlay()
  {
    return mHighlightOverlay;
  }

private:
  Dali::Ui::AccessibilityHighlightOverlay mHighlightOverlay;
};
```

## 사용 Automatic Highlight Placement {#use-automatic-highlight-placement}

호출할 항목: `UpdateOverlay` 경우 the active accessibility highlight changes. In automatic mode, `AccessibilityHighlightOverlay` finds the parent SceneView 위해 the supplied highlight actor 및 positions the overlay에서 the highlighted model bounds.

`UpdateOverlay` takes the active highlight로 `Dali::Actor&` 때문에 this integration API works와(과) 함께 the highlight actor passed를 통해 the accessibility layer. In 애플리케이션 structure, keep the rest의 the UI modeled로 `Dali::Ui::View`.

```cpp
#include <dali-ui-foundation/integration-api/accessibility-highlight-overlay.h>

class AccessibilityOverlayController
{
public:
  void OnActiveHighlightChanged(Dali::Actor& activeHighlight)
  {
    mHighlightOverlay.UpdateOverlay(activeHighlight);
  }

private:
  Dali::Ui::AccessibilityHighlightOverlay mHighlightOverlay;
};
```

You can explicitly return the controller에 automatic placement를 통해 calling `ResetCustomHighlight` 전에 the next `UpdateOverlay`.

```cpp
#include <dali-ui-foundation/integration-api/accessibility-highlight-overlay.h>

void UseAutomaticHighlight(
  Dali::Ui::AccessibilityHighlightOverlay& highlightOverlay,
  Dali::Actor& activeHighlight)
{
  highlightOverlay.ResetCustomHighlight();
  highlightOverlay.UpdateOverlay(activeHighlight);
}
```

## 사용 a Custom Highlight Rectangle {#use-a-custom-highlight-rectangle}

사용할 항목: `SetCustomHighlight` 경우 the 비주얼 highlight rectangle should be placed at a 특정 위치 및 크기 within the overlay. 해당 메서드 받습니다 a `Dali::Vector2` 위치 및 a `Dali::Vector2` 크기.

```cpp
#include <dali-ui-foundation/integration-api/accessibility-highlight-overlay.h>

void HighlightCustomRegion(
  Dali::Ui::AccessibilityHighlightOverlay& highlightOverlay,
  Dali::Actor& activeHighlight)
{
  const Dali::Vector2 overlayPosition(24.0f, 32.0f);
  const Dali::Vector2 overlaySize(220.0f, 72.0f);

  highlightOverlay.SetCustomHighlight(overlayPosition, overlaySize);
  highlightOverlay.UpdateOverlay(activeHighlight);
}
```

`SetCustomHighlight` also switches the overlay로 manual placement mode. After setting the 사용자 지정 rectangle, call `UpdateOverlay`와(과) 함께 the 현재 active highlight 그래서 the visible overlay는 refreshed.

```cpp
#include <dali-ui-foundation/integration-api/accessibility-highlight-overlay.h>

class ManualAccessibilityHighlight
{
public:
  void Show(Dali::Actor& activeHighlight)
  {
    mHighlightOverlay.SetCustomHighlight(
      Dali::Vector2(8.0f, 8.0f),
      Dali::Vector2(180.0f, 56.0f));

    mHighlightOverlay.UpdateOverlay(activeHighlight);
  }

private:
  Dali::Ui::AccessibilityHighlightOverlay mHighlightOverlay;
};
```

## Reset or 숨기기 the Overlay {#reset-or-hide-the-overlay}

호출할 항목: `ResetCustomHighlight` 경우 a manual rectangle should no longer be used. 해당 메서드 clears the stored manual rectangle 및 반환합니다 the mode에 automatic placement.

```cpp
#include <dali-ui-foundation/integration-api/accessibility-highlight-overlay.h>

void ReturnToAutomaticPlacement(
  Dali::Ui::AccessibilityHighlightOverlay& highlightOverlay,
  Dali::Actor& activeHighlight)
{
  highlightOverlay.ResetCustomHighlight();
  highlightOverlay.UpdateOverlay(activeHighlight);
}
```

호출할 항목: `HideOverlay` 경우 the 현재 highlight should no longer be displayed, such로 경우 the accessibility 포커스 leaves the relevant 뷰 area.

```cpp
#include <dali-ui-foundation/integration-api/accessibility-highlight-overlay.h>

class AccessibilityOverlayController
{
public:
  void ShowFor(Dali::Actor& activeHighlight)
  {
    mHighlightOverlay.UpdateOverlay(activeHighlight);
  }

  void Hide()
  {
    mHighlightOverlay.HideOverlay();
  }

private:
  Dali::Ui::AccessibilityHighlightOverlay mHighlightOverlay;
};
```

`HideOverlay` hides the overlay highlight actor 경우 one exists. It does not clear a 사용자 지정 rectangle 또는 change the overlay mode. 다음 경우에는 you want the next highlight update에 return에 automatic placement, call `ResetCustomHighlight`로 well.

```cpp
#include <dali-ui-foundation/integration-api/accessibility-highlight-overlay.h>

void ClearManualOverlayState(Dali::Ui::AccessibilityHighlightOverlay& highlightOverlay)
{
  highlightOverlay.HideOverlay();
  highlightOverlay.ResetCustomHighlight();
}
```

## 조회 and Preserve Overlay Mode {#query-and-preserve-overlay-mode}

사용할 항목: `GetOverlayMode` 경우 your controller needs에 inspect the 현재 placement mode, 위해 example 전에 temporarily changing how the overlay는 updated.

```cpp
#include <dali-ui-foundation/integration-api/accessibility-highlight-overlay.h>

Dali::Ui::OverlayHighlightMode ReadCurrentMode(
  const Dali::Ui::AccessibilityHighlightOverlay& highlightOverlay)
{
  return highlightOverlay.GetOverlayMode();
}
```

사용할 항목: `SetOverlayMode` 경우 restoring a previously saved mode 값.

```cpp
#include <dali-ui-foundation/integration-api/accessibility-highlight-overlay.h>

class OverlayModeScope
{
public:
  explicit OverlayModeScope(Dali::Ui::AccessibilityHighlightOverlay& highlightOverlay)
  : mHighlightOverlay(highlightOverlay),
    mSavedMode(highlightOverlay.GetOverlayMode())
  {
  }

  ~OverlayModeScope()
  {
    mHighlightOverlay.SetOverlayMode(mSavedMode);
  }

private:
  Dali::Ui::AccessibilityHighlightOverlay& mHighlightOverlay;
  Dali::Ui::OverlayHighlightMode mSavedMode;
};
```

다음에 대해 일반 app flows, prefer the higher-level 상태 changes: `SetCustomHighlight` 위해 manual placement 및 `ResetCustomHighlight` 위해 automatic placement. 사용할 항목: `SetOverlayMode` only 경우 your code는 intentionally preserving 또는 restoring the mode 값; it does not restore a previous manual 위치 또는 크기.

