# 애드온 관리자 {#addon-manager}

Addon 관리자 lets a DALi 애플리케이션 discover, inspect, load, 및 call platform-provided add-on libraries through `Dali::Integration::AddOnManager`.

## 목차 {#table-of-contents}

- [Where Addon 관리자 Fits에서 a dali-ui App.](#where-addon-manager-fits-in-a-dali-ui-app)
- [Discovering 사용 가능한 Add-ons.](#discovering-available-add-ons)
- [애드온 메타데이터 읽기](#reading-add-on-metadata)
- [Loading an Add-on 및 Calling Global Procedures.](#loading-an-add-on-and-calling-global-procedures)
- [명시적 라이브러리 로딩 사용](#using-explicit-library-loading)
- [생명주기 전달](#lifecycle-forwarding)

## Where 애드온 관리자 Fits in a dali-ui App {#where-addon-manager-fits-in-a-dali-ui-app}

dali-ui 애플리케이션 should keep its user interface에서 the `Dali::Ui::View` tree 및 use Addon 관리자 only 위해 platform integration work, such로 loading optional functionality 또는 resolving add-on procedures. 해당 app-facing UI 객체 model stays 뷰-based; `Dali::Integration::AddOnManager`는 service 객체 obtained에서 its singleton.

```cpp
#include <dali/integration-api/addon-manager.h>

void UseAddOnsFromViewCode()
{
  Dali::Integration::AddOnManager* manager = Dali::Integration::AddOnManager::Get();
  if(!manager)
  {
    return;
  }

  const std::vector<std::string> addOnNames = manager->EnumerateAddOns();
  for(const std::string& name : addOnNames)
  {
    // Use add-on availability to decide which dali-ui View behavior to enable.
  }
}
```

`Dali::Integration::AddOnManager::Get()` 반환합니다 the 관리자 created를 통해 the adaptor. 다음 경우에는 the platform 또는 test environment has not installed an Addon 관리자 implementation, the returned 포인터 can be `nullptr`.

## Discovering Available 추가-ons {#discovering-available-add-ons}

사용할 항목: `Dali::Integration::AddOnManager::EnumerateAddOns()`에 ask the platform implementation 위해 the 사용 가능한 add-on names. 해당 result는 `std::vector<std::string>` containing names that can be passed에 `Dali::Integration::AddOnManager::GetAddOnInfo()`, `Dali::Integration::AddOnManager::LoadAddOns()`, 또는 `Dali::Integration::AddOnManager::GetAddOn()`.

```cpp
#include <dali/integration-api/addon-manager.h>

std::vector<std::string> GetAvailableAddOns()
{
  Dali::Integration::AddOnManager* manager = Dali::Integration::AddOnManager::Get();
  if(!manager)
  {
    return {};
  }

  return manager->EnumerateAddOns();
}
```

다음에 대해 a dali-ui app, discovery는 usually done 동안 기능 setup. 해당 UI can 그런 다음 expose only the actions backed를 통해 사용 가능한 add-ons, 동안 the 비주얼 hierarchy remains 기반으로 `Dali::Ui::View`.

## Reading 추가-on Metadata {#reading-add-on-metadata}

`Dali::AddOnInfo` describes an add-on. `Dali::Integration::AddOnManager::GetAddOnInfo()` fills a caller-provided `Dali::AddOnInfo` 및 반환합니다 `true` 경우 the information was retrieved.

해당 metadata fields는 stored에서 `Dali::AddOnInfo`:

- `Dali::AddOnInfo::type`
- `Dali::AddOnInfo::next`
- `Dali::AddOnInfo::name`
- `Dali::AddOnInfo::version`
- `Dali::AddOnInfo::buildInfo`

Build version fields는 grouped under `Dali::AddOnInfo::BuildInfo`:

- `Dali::AddOnInfo::BuildInfo::libCoreVersion`

