-`Dali::Ui::ScrollBarVisibility::Auto` shows the bar 동안 scrolling. `Dali::Ui::ScrollBarVisibility::Always` 유지합니다 it visible. `Dali::Ui::ScrollBarVisibility::Never` disables that axis.
