# 이미지 로더 {#image-loader}

`Dali::Ui::AsyncImageLoader` 로드합니다 이미지 pixel data에서 URLs asynchronously 위해 dali-ui apps, 및 `Dali::Ui::ImageUrl` 노출합니다 externally supplied 이미지 리소스, such로 encoded 이미지 buffers, through URL strings.

## 목차 {#table-of-contents}

- [Loading 이미지 data 없이 blocking the UI.](#loading-image-data-without-blocking-the-ui)
- [Matching load results에 a `Dali::Ui::View`.](#matching-load-results-to-a-daliuiview)
- [오래된 요청 취소](#cancelling-obsolete-requests)
- [Using encoded buffers로 이미지 URLs.](#using-encoded-buffers-as-image-urls)
- [Working와(과) 함께 이미지-loader handles.](#working-with-image-loader-handles)

## UI를 막지 않고 이미지 데이터 로드 {#loading-image-data-without-blocking-the-ui}

생성할 항목: a loader와(과) 함께 `Dali::Ui::AsyncImageLoader::New()`. 해당 loader starts 이미지 loading work에서 a worker thread; your `Dali::Ui::View` owner should keep the loader alive 위해로 long로 pending 이미지 requests can complete.

연결할 항목: `Dali::Ui::AsyncImageLoader::ImageLoadedSignal()` 전에 calling `Dali::Ui::AsyncImageLoader::Load()`. 해당 시그널 내보냅니다 the task ID returned에서 `Load()` 및 the loaded pixel data, 그래서 the 콜백 can decide which 뷰 상태에 update.

```cpp
class ThumbnailLoader
{
public:
  explicit ThumbnailLoader(Dali::Ui::View ownerView)
  : mOwnerView(ownerView),
    mLoader(Dali::Ui::AsyncImageLoader::New())
  {
    mLoader.ImageLoadedSignal().Connect(this, &ThumbnailLoader::OnImageLoaded);
  }

  void LoadThumbnail(const Dali::String& imageUrl)
  {
    mTaskId = mLoader.Load(imageUrl, Dali::ImageDimensions(160u, 160u));
  }

private:
  void OnImageLoaded(uint32_t loadedTaskId, Dali::PixelData pixelData)
  {
    if(loadedTaskId != mTaskId)
    {
      return;
    }

    if(pixelData)
    {
      // Use the loaded pixel data to update image presentation owned by mOwnerView.
    }
  }

  Dali::Ui::View             mOwnerView;
  Dali::Ui::AsyncImageLoader mLoader;
  uint32_t                   mTaskId{0u};
};
```

`Dali::Ui::AsyncImageLoader::Load()` has a 크기-aware form that 받습니다 `Dali::ImageDimensions`. 사용할 항목: this 경우 the 뷰 already knows the intended 이미지 크기, such로 a thumbnail, tile, 또는 avatar slot.

```cpp
uint32_t RequestTileImage(Dali::Ui::AsyncImageLoader& loader, const Dali::String& url)
{
  return loader.Load(url, Dali::ImageDimensions(320u, 180u));
}
```

## 로드 결과를 다음과 매칭: `Dali::Ui::View` {#matching-load-results-to-a-daliuiview}

single `Dali::Ui::AsyncImageLoader` can start more than one request. 저장할 항목: each task ID returned를 통해 `Dali::Ui::AsyncImageLoader::Load()` 및 compare it에서 the 콜백 connected through `Dali::Ui::AsyncImageLoader::ImageLoadedSignal()`.

이는는 especially important 경우 a `Dali::Ui::View`는 reused 위해 changing data, such로 a gallery cell 또는 search 결과 row. older request may complete 후에 the 뷰 has been rebound에 a different 이미지.

```cpp
class ProfileImageSet
{
public:
  explicit ProfileImageSet(Dali::Ui::View ownerView)
  : mOwnerView(ownerView),
    mLoader(Dali::Ui::AsyncImageLoader::New())
  {
    mLoader.ImageLoadedSignal().Connect(this, &ProfileImageSet::OnImageLoaded);
  }

  void LoadImages(const Dali::String& avatarUrl, const Dali::String& bannerUrl)
  {
    mAvatarTaskId = mLoader.Load(avatarUrl, Dali::ImageDimensions(96u, 96u));
    mBannerTaskId = mLoader.Load(bannerUrl, Dali::ImageDimensions(640u, 240u));
  }

private:
  void OnImageLoaded(uint32_t loadedTaskId, Dali::PixelData pixelData)
  {
    if(!pixelData)
    {
      return;
    }

    if(loadedTaskId == mAvatarTaskId)
    {
      // Apply avatar pixel data to the avatar presentation for mOwnerView.
      return;
    }

    if(loadedTaskId == mBannerTaskId)
    {
      // Apply banner pixel data to the banner presentation for mOwnerView.
      return;
    }
  }

  Dali::Ui::View             mOwnerView;
  Dali::Ui::AsyncImageLoader mLoader;
  uint32_t                   mAvatarTaskId{0u};
  uint32_t                   mBannerTaskId{0u};
};
```

해당 콜백 should treat an invalid pixel data handle로 a load failure. 유지할 항목: failure handling local에 the owning 뷰 또는 controller, 때문에 `Dali::Ui::AsyncImageLoader` reports completion 및 loaded data rather than deciding how the app should present errors.

## 오래된 요청 취소 {#cancelling-obsolete-requests}

사용할 항목: `Dali::Ui::AsyncImageLoader::Cancel()` 경우 one request는 no longer useful. It 반환합니다 `true` 경우 the task는 removed 동안 it는 still queued. 다음 경우에는 loading has already progressed far enough that it cannot be removed, `Cancel()` 반환합니다 `false`.

```cpp
class SearchResultImage
{
public:
  explicit SearchResultImage(Dali::Ui::View ownerView)
  : mOwnerView(ownerView),
    mLoader(Dali::Ui::AsyncImageLoader::New())
  {
    mLoader.ImageLoadedSignal().Connect(this, &SearchResultImage::OnImageLoaded);
  }

  void ReplaceImage(const Dali::String& nextUrl)
  {
    if(mTaskId != 0u)
    {
      const bool removedFromQueue = mLoader.Cancel(mTaskId);
      (void)removedFromQueue;
    }

    mTaskId = mLoader.Load(nextUrl, Dali::ImageDimensions(240u, 240u));
  }

private:
  void OnImageLoaded(uint32_t loadedTaskId, Dali::PixelData pixelData)
  {
    if(loadedTaskId == mTaskId && pixelData)
    {
      // Update the current search-result image presentation.
    }
  }

  Dali::Ui::View             mOwnerView;
  Dali::Ui::AsyncImageLoader mLoader;
  uint32_t                   mTaskId{0u};
};
```

사용할 항목: `Dali::Ui::AsyncImageLoader::CancelAll()` 경우 all queued work tracked를 통해 the loader는 obsolete, such로 경우 clearing a list, replacing a gallery data source, 또는 destroying the owner.

```cpp
class GalleryPageImages
{
public:
  explicit GalleryPageImages(Dali::Ui::View pageView)
  : mPageView(pageView),
    mLoader(Dali::Ui::AsyncImageLoader::New())
  {
    mLoader.ImageLoadedSignal().Connect(this, &GalleryPageImages::OnImageLoaded);
  }

  ~GalleryPageImages()
  {
    mLoader.CancelAll();
  }

  void Reset()
  {
    mLoader.CancelAll();
    mHeroTaskId = 0u;
  }

private:
  void OnImageLoaded(uint32_t loadedTaskId, Dali::PixelData pixelData)
  {
    if(loadedTaskId == mHeroTaskId && pixelData)
    {
      // Apply the loaded hero image for mPageView.
    }
  }

  Dali::Ui::View             mPageView;
  Dali::Ui::AsyncImageLoader mLoader;
  uint32_t                   mHeroTaskId{0u};
};
```

## 인코딩된 버퍼를 이미지 URL로 사용 {#using-encoded-buffers-as-image-urls}

`Dali::Ui::ImageUrl` can wrap an encoded 이미지 buffer 및 provide a URL string through `Dali::Ui::ImageUrl::GetUrl()`. 생성할 항목: it와(과) 함께 `Dali::Ui::ImageUrl::New()` 및 keep the returned handle alive 동안 the generated URL는 still being used를 통해 the app's 이미지 presentation.

```cpp
class EncodedPreviewImage
{
public:
  explicit EncodedPreviewImage(Dali::Ui::View ownerView)
  : mOwnerView(ownerView)
  {
  }

  const Dali::String& UseEncodedBuffer(const Dali::EncodedImageBuffer& encodedImageBuffer)
