# 이미지 뷰 {#image-view}

`Dali::Ui::ImageView` displays an 이미지 리소스에서 a dali-ui 뷰 tree,와(과) 함께 app-facing 제어합니다 위해 fitting, sampling, masking, loading, 및 rendering 동작. 이미지 loading는 asynchronous를 통해 기본.

## 목차 {#table-of-contents}

- [생성할 항목: 및 설정할 항목: an 이미지 Source.](#create-and-set-an-image-source)
- [Fit, Sample, 및 Load at a Desired 크기.](#fit-sample-and-load-at-a-desired-size)
- [Tint 및 Crop the Displayed 이미지 Region.](#tint-and-crop-the-displayed-image-region)
- [사용할 항목: 플레이스홀더 이미지 및 Loading 시그널.](#use-placeholder-images-and-loading-signals)
- [알파 마스크 적용](#apply-alpha-masks)
- [Tune Loading 및 Release 동작.](#tune-loading-and-release-behavior)
- [N-Patch 테두리 렌더링](#render-n-patch-borders)
- [속성 Constants.](#property-constants)

## 생성 and 설정 an 이미지 Source {#create-and-set-an-image-source}

생성할 항목: an initialized `Dali::Ui::ImageView`와(과) 함께 `Dali::Ui::ImageView::New()`, 그런 다음 set the 이미지 URL와(과) 함께 `SetResourceUrl`. You can also pass the URL에 `Dali::Ui::ImageView::New(const Dali::String&)` 경우 the source는 known at construction time. 해당 현재 URL는 사용 가능한 through `GetResourceUrl`, 및 `Reload` reloads the 현재 URL 경우 one has been set.

```cpp
Dali::Ui::ImageView thumbnail = Dali::Ui::ImageView::New();

thumbnail
  .SetResourceUrl("images/profile.png")
  .SetFittingMode(Dali::Ui::Image::FittingMode::FIT_KEEP_ASPECT_RATIO);

Dali::String currentUrl = thumbnail.GetResourceUrl();

thumbnail.Reload();
```

사용할 항목: `Dali::Ui::ImageView::DownCast` 경우 a 콜백 또는 container gives you a `Dali::Ui::View` 및 you need `ImageView`-특정 APIs.

```cpp
void UpdateImageSource(Dali::Ui::View view, const Dali::String& nextUrl)
{
  Dali::Ui::ImageView imageView = Dali::Ui::ImageView::DownCast(view);
  if(imageView)
  {
    imageView.SetResourceUrl(nextUrl);
  }
}
```

## Fit, Sample, and 로드 at a Desired Size {#fit-sample-and-load-at-a-desired-size}

`SetFittingMode` 제어합니다 how the 이미지는 fitted로 the 뷰 bounds. 사용할 항목: `Dali::Ui::Image::FittingMode::FIT_KEEP_ASPECT_RATIO` 경우 preserving aspect ratio matters, `Dali::Ui::Image::FittingMode::FILL` 경우 stretching에 the 사용 가능한 bounds는 acceptable, `Dali::Ui::Image::FittingMode::OVER_FIT_KEEP_ASPECT_RATIO` 경우 cropping outside the bounds는 preferred, 및 `Dali::Ui::Image::FittingMode::CENTER` 경우 the 이미지 should keep its original 크기.

`SetSamplingMode` 제어합니다 the filtering used 경우 scaling. `SetDesiredWidth` 및 `SetDesiredHeight` provide rasterization 크기 hints에서 pixels,와(과) 함께 `0` meaning the natural 크기.

```cpp
Dali::Ui::ImageView preview = Dali::Ui::ImageView::New();

preview
  .SetResourceUrl("images/gallery/large-photo.jpg")
  .SetFittingMode(Dali::Ui::Image::FittingMode::FIT_KEEP_ASPECT_RATIO)
  .SetSamplingMode(Dali::Ui::Image::SamplingMode::BOX_THEN_LINEAR)
  .SetDesiredWidth(480)
  .SetDesiredHeight(320);

Dali::Ui::Image::FittingMode fittingMode = preview.GetFittingMode();
Dali::Ui::Image::SamplingMode samplingMode = preview.GetSamplingMode();
int desiredWidth = preview.GetDesiredWidth();
int desiredHeight = preview.GetDesiredHeight();
```

다음 경우에는 the final 뷰 크기 should drive the 이미지 load 크기, enable `SetImageLoadWithViewSize`. 이는 로드합니다 the 이미지 at the resolved 뷰 크기 매번 the 뷰 크기 changes, which avoids loading the full-resolution 리소스 위해 a smaller display area. Do not combine this와(과) 함께 aspect-ratio 레이아웃에서 the 동일한 `ImageView`, 때문에 the natural 크기 reported 위해 레이아웃 becomes the 현재 뷰 크기 대신 the source 이미지 dimensions.

```cpp
Dali::Ui::ImageView cardImage = Dali::Ui::ImageView::New();

cardImage
  .SetResourceUrl("images/card-cover.jpg")
  .SetFittingMode(Dali::Ui::Image::FittingMode::OVER_FIT_KEEP_ASPECT_RATIO)
  .SetImageLoadWithViewSize(true);

bool loadWithViewSize = cardImage.IsImageLoadWithViewSizeEnabled();
```

## Tint and Crop the Displayed 이미지 Region {#tint-and-crop-the-displayed-image-region}

사용할 항목: `SetImageColor`에 apply a 색상 multiplier에 the 이미지. 사용할 항목: `SetPixelArea`에 display a normalized sub-region의 the source 이미지, expressed로 `(x, y, width, height)`.

```cpp
Dali::Ui::ImageView icon = Dali::Ui::ImageView::New();

icon
  .SetResourceUrl("images/icons/search.png")
  .SetImageColor(Dali::Ui::UiColor(1.0f, 1.0f, 1.0f, 0.65f))
  .SetPreMultipliedAlpha(true);

Dali::Ui::UiColor tint = icon.GetImageColor();
bool preMultiplied = icon.IsPreMultipliedAlpha();
```

```cpp
Dali::Ui::ImageView atlasImage = Dali::Ui::ImageView::New();

atlasImage
  .SetResourceUrl("images/sprite-atlas.png")
  .SetPixelArea(Dali::Vector4(0.25f, 0.0f, 0.25f, 0.5f))
  .SetFittingMode(Dali::Ui::Image::FittingMode::FILL);

Dali::Vector4 displayedArea = atlasImage.GetPixelArea();
```

## 사용 플레이스홀더 Images and Loading 시그널 {#use-placeholder-images-and-loading-signals}

설정할 항목: `SetPlaceholderUrl` 경우 you want a temporary 이미지 동안 the main 이미지 로드합니다. `ResourceReadySignal`는 emitted와(과) 함께 a `Dali::Ui::View` parameter 경우 the 리소스는 ready에 display, 및 `GetLoadingStatus` 반환합니다 the 현재 `Dali::Ui::Visual::ResourceStatus`.

```cpp
class ImageController : public Dali::ConnectionTracker
{
public:
  Dali::Ui::ImageView CreateImage()
  {
    Dali::Ui::ImageView imageView = Dali::Ui::ImageView::New();

    imageView
      .SetPlaceholderUrl("images/placeholder.png")
      .SetResourceUrl("images/remote-photo.jpg")
      .SetFittingMode(Dali::Ui::Image::FittingMode::FIT_KEEP_ASPECT_RATIO);

    imageView.ResourceReadySignal().Connect(this, &ImageController::OnResourceReady);

    return imageView;
  }

private:
  void OnResourceReady(Dali::Ui::View view)
  {
    Dali::Ui::ImageView imageView = Dali::Ui::ImageView::DownCast(view);
    if(imageView)
    {
      Dali::Ui::Visual::ResourceStatus status = imageView.GetLoadingStatus();
      (void)status;
    }
  }
};
```

`GetPlaceholderUrl` lets you inspect the configured placeholder URL.

```cpp
Dali::Ui::ImageView imageView = Dali::Ui::ImageView::New();

imageView.SetPlaceholderUrl("images/loading.png");

Dali::String placeholderUrl = imageView.GetPlaceholderUrl();
```

## 적용 Alpha Masks {#apply-alpha-masks}

`SetAlphaMaskUrl` 적용합니다 the alpha channel의 a mask 이미지에 the main 이미지. `SetCropToMask` 제어합니다 whether the 이미지는 cropped에 the mask bounds. `SetMaskingMode` selects whether masking는 applied 동안 rendering 또는 동안 loading.

```cpp
Dali::Ui::ImageView avatar = Dali::Ui::ImageView::New();

avatar
  .SetResourceUrl("images/profile-photo.jpg")
  .SetAlphaMaskUrl("images/masks/circle-mask.png")
  .SetCropToMask(true)
  .SetMaskingMode(Dali::Ui::Image::MaskingType::MASKING_ON_RENDERING)
  .SetFittingMode(Dali::Ui::Image::FittingMode::OVER_FIT_KEEP_ASPECT_RATIO);

Dali::String maskUrl = avatar.GetAlphaMaskUrl();
bool cropToMask = avatar.IsCropToMask();
Dali::Ui::Image::MaskingType maskingMode = avatar.GetMaskingMode();
```

사용할 항목: `Dali::Ui::Image::MaskingType::MASKING_ON_LOADING` 경우 you want the masked 결과 prepared로 part의 loading.

```cpp
Dali::Ui::ImageView maskedThumbnail = Dali::Ui::ImageView::New();

maskedThumbnail
  .SetResourceUrl("images/thumbnail.jpg")
  .SetAlphaMaskUrl("images/masks/rounded-rect.png")
  .SetMaskingMode(Dali::Ui::Image::MaskingType::MASKING_ON_LOADING);
```

## Tune Loading and Release Behavior {#tune-loading-and-release-behavior}

`SetLoadPolicy` 제어합니다 경우 loading begins. `Dali::Ui::Image::LoadPolicy::IMMEDIATE` 로드합니다 경우 the 이미지 view는 created, 동안 `Dali::Ui::Image::LoadPolicy::ATTACHED` defers loading until the view는 attached에 the scene.

`SetReleasePolicy` 제어합니다 경우 the texture는 released에서 cache. 사용할 항목: `Dali::Ui::Image::ReleasePolicy::DETACHED`, `Dali::Ui::Image::ReleasePolicy::DESTROYED`, 또는 `Dali::Ui::Image::ReleasePolicy::NEVER` according에 the 수명 및 reuse pattern의 the 이미지. `SetFastTrackUpload` enables the fast-track upload 경로 위해 eligible 이미지 리소스; 위해 that 경로, use `LoadPolicy::ATTACHED`와(과) 함께 `ReleasePolicy::DETACHED`, 및 avoid synchronous loading 또는 alpha-mask loading에서 the 동일한 이미지.

```cpp
Dali::Ui::ImageView reusableImage = Dali::Ui::ImageView::New();

reusableImage
  .SetResourceUrl("images/navigation/background.jpg")
  .SetLoadPolicy(Dali::Ui::Image::LoadPolicy::ATTACHED)
  .SetReleasePolicy(Dali::Ui::Image::ReleasePolicy::DETACHED)
  .SetFastTrackUpload(true)
  .SetOrientationCorrection(true);

Dali::Ui::Image::LoadPolicy loadPolicy = reusableImage.GetLoadPolicy();
Dali::Ui::Image::ReleasePolicy releasePolicy = reusableImage.GetReleasePolicy();
bool fastTrackUpload = reusableImage.IsFastTrackUploadEnabled();
bool orientationCorrection = reusableImage.IsOrientationCorrectionEnabled();
```

다음에 대해 cases where blocking load 동작는 acceptable, `SetSynchronousLoading` enables synchronous 이미지 loading에서 the main thread.

```cpp
Dali::Ui::ImageView immediateIcon = Dali::Ui::ImageView::New();

immediateIcon
  .SetSynchronousLoading(true)
  .SetResourceUrl("images/icons/local-action.png");

bool synchronous = immediateIcon.IsSynchronousLoading();
```

## N-Patch 테두리 렌더링 {#render-n-patch-borders}

사용할 항목: `SetNPatchBorder` 위해 scalable panel 이미지 that preserve fixed edge regions. 해당 border는 expressed로 `(left, top, right, bottom)` pixel 값, 및 setting a non-zero border activates N-patch rendering. `SetNPatchBorderOnly` renders only the border regions 경우 the center should be omitted.

```cpp
Dali::Ui::ImageView panel = Dali::Ui::ImageView::New();

panel
  .SetResourceUrl("images/panels/dialog.9.png")
  .SetNPatchBorder(Dali::Vector4(12.0f, 12.0f, 12.0f, 12.0f))
  .SetNPatchBorderOnly(false);

Dali::Vector4 border = panel.GetNPatchBorder();
bool borderOnly = panel.IsNPatchBorderOnly();
```

`SetDepthIndex` adjusts the rendering order의 the 이미지 비주얼 within the 동일한 layer; higher 값 render above lower 값.

