# 입력 이벤트 {#input-event}

`Dali::Ui::InputEvent` 식별합니다 the input 또는 non-input cause behind dali-ui interaction 및 상태 changes.

## 목차 {#table-of-contents}

- [다음의 의미: `InputEvent` 나타냅니다.](#what-inputevent-represents)
- [입력 원인 생성](#creating-an-input-cause)
- [Reading the Typed 이벤트 Payload.](#reading-the-typed-event-payload)
- [비입력 원인 사용](#using-a-non-input-cause)
- [Passing Input 이벤트 Through 뷰 로직.](#passing-input-events-through-view-logic)

## 다음의 의미: `InputEvent` Represents {#what-inputevent-represents}

In a dali-ui 애플리케이션, 뷰 interaction 로직 often needs에 know why a 상태 changed. `Dali::Ui::InputEvent`는 the app-facing handle 위해 that cause. It can represent a concrete input payload, such로 a touch 이벤트, key 이벤트, tap 제스처, long-press 제스처, 또는 wheel 이벤트, 또는 it can represent a non-input change.

사용할 항목: `GetInputEventType()` 전에 deciding which typed getter는 valid 위해 a particular `Dali::Ui::InputEvent`.

```cpp
#include <dali-ui-foundation/public-api/input-event.h>

void StoreLastInputCause(const Dali::Ui::InputEvent& event)
{
  Dali::Ui::InputEvent lastEvent;
  lastEvent = event;

  auto eventType = lastEvent.GetInputEventType();
  (void)eventType;
}
```

`Dali::Ui::InputEvent`는 handle 타입. Copying 또는 assigning it와(과) 함께 `operator=` 유지합니다 a reference에 the 동일한 이벤트 handle rather than copying each payload field manually.

## 입력 원인 생성 {#creating-an-input-cause}

다음 경우에는 code already has a concrete input 객체, create a `Dali::Ui::InputEvent`와(과) 함께 the matching `InputEvent::New()` overload. 다음에 대해 wheel input, pass the source `Dali::WheelEvent` directly.

```cpp
#include <dali-ui-foundation/public-api/input-event.h>
#include <dali/public-api/events/wheel-event.h>

Dali::Ui::InputEvent MakeWheelCause(const Dali::WheelEvent& wheelEvent)
{
  return Dali::Ui::InputEvent::New(wheelEvent);
}
```

created 이벤트 can 그런 다음 be passed through your dali-ui 뷰 controller 또는 상태 로직로 a single cause 객체.

```cpp
#include <dali-ui-foundation/public-api/input-event.h>
#include <dali/public-api/events/wheel-event.h>

class ViewInteractionController
{
public:
  void OnWheel(const Dali::WheelEvent& wheelEvent)
  {
    Dali::Ui::InputEvent cause = Dali::Ui::InputEvent::New(wheelEvent);
    RememberCause(cause);
  }

private:
  void RememberCause(const Dali::Ui::InputEvent& cause)
  {
    mLastCause = cause;
  }

  Dali::Ui::InputEvent mLastCause;
};
```

## 타입화된 이벤트 페이로드 읽기 {#reading-the-typed-event-payload}

`Dali::Ui::InputEvent` 저장합니다 the original 이벤트 payload. 사용할 항목: the getter that matches the 이벤트 타입 you는 handling. 다음에 대해 a `Dali::Ui::InputEvent` whose type는 `Dali::Ui::InputEventType::WHEEL_EVENT`, use `GetWheelEvent()`.

```cpp
#include <dali-ui-foundation/public-api/input-event.h>
#include <dali/public-api/events/wheel-event.h>

const Dali::WheelEvent& ReadWheelEvent(const Dali::Ui::InputEvent& event)
{
  return event.GetWheelEvent();
}
```

해당 typed getters return const references에 the stored payload 및 assert if the stored 타입 does not match the getter:

```cpp
#include <dali-ui-foundation/public-api/input-event.h>

void ReadKnownTypedInput(const Dali::Ui::InputEvent& event)
{
  auto inputType = event.GetInputEventType();
  (void)inputType;

  // Call the typed getter that matches the input type used by this code path.
  // Examples:
  // const auto& touchEvent = event.GetTouchEvent();
  // const auto& keyEvent = event.GetKeyEvent();
  // const auto& tapGesture = event.GetTapGesture();
  // const auto& longPressGesture = event.GetLongPressGesture();
  const auto& wheelEvent = event.GetWheelEvent();
  (void)wheelEvent;
}
```

사용할 항목: `GetTouchEvent()`, `GetKeyEvent()`, `GetTapGesture()`, `GetLongPressGesture()`, 및 `GetWheelEvent()` only에서 이벤트 created에서 the corresponding source input.

## 비입력 원인 사용 {#using-a-non-input-cause}

Not every 뷰 상태 change comes에서 직접 user input. 사용할 항목: `InputEvent::None()` 경우 a valid shared `Dali::Ui::InputEvent`는 needed but the change는 programmatic 또는 framework-triggered.

```cpp
#include <dali-ui-foundation/public-api/input-event.h>

const Dali::Ui::InputEvent& ProgrammaticCause()
{
  return Dali::Ui::InputEvent::None();
}
```

`InputEvent::None()` 반환합니다 a shared const reference와(과) 함께 `Dali::Ui::InputEventType::NONE`, 그래서 it는 suitable 위해 repeated non-input 경로. 사용할 항목: `InputEvent::New()`와(과) 함께 no arguments only 경우 you need a 별도의 `NONE` 이벤트 handle.

```cpp
#include <dali-ui-foundation/public-api/input-event.h>

class ViewStateController
{
public:
  void MarkChangedByCode()
  {
    ApplyCause(Dali::Ui::InputEvent::None());
  }

private:
  void ApplyCause(const Dali::Ui::InputEvent& cause)
  {
    mLastCause = cause;
  }

  Dali::Ui::InputEvent mLastCause;
};
```

## Passing Input 이벤트 Through 뷰 Logic {#passing-input-events-through-view-logic}

유지할 항목: `Dali::Ui::InputEvent` at the boundary between input handling 및 뷰 상태 로직. Your dali-ui code can receive concrete input, wrap it once, 및 pass the cause through helpers that operate에서 `Dali::Ui::View`-based 애플리케이션 객체.

```cpp
#include <dali-ui-foundation/public-api/input-event.h>
#include <dali-ui-foundation/public-api/view.h>
#include <dali/public-api/events/wheel-event.h>

class ScrollableViewController
{
public:
  explicit ScrollableViewController(Dali::Ui::View view)
  : mView(view)
  {
  }

  void HandleWheelInput(const Dali::WheelEvent& wheelEvent)
  {
    Dali::Ui::InputEvent cause = Dali::Ui::InputEvent::New(wheelEvent);
    UpdateFromInput(cause);
  }

  void HandleProgrammaticUpdate()
  {
    UpdateFromInput(Dali::Ui::InputEvent::None());
  }

private:
  void UpdateFromInput(const Dali::Ui::InputEvent& cause)
  {
    mLastCause = cause;
    auto causeType = mLastCause.GetInputEventType();
    (void)causeType;
  }

  Dali::Ui::View mView;
  Dali::Ui::InputEvent mLastCause;
};
```

이는 유지합니다 the 애플리케이션 model centered에서 `Dali::Ui::View` 동안 preserving the exact input cause 위해 interaction-특정 decisions.

