# 인터랙티브 뷰 {#interactive-view}

`Dali::Ui::InteractiveView`는 the dali-ui `View` 타입 위해 clickable, press-aware UI surfaces.

## 목차 {#table-of-contents}

- [생성할 항목: an Interactive Surface.](#create-an-interactive-surface)
- [클릭 처리](#handle-clicks)
- [Control 키보드 Click Timing.](#control-keyboard-click-timing)
- [Track Pressed 및 Pseudo Disabled 상태.](#track-pressed-and-pseudo-disabled-state)
- [길게 누르기 처리](#handle-long-press)
- [사용할 항목: InteractiveView에서 Typed Handles.](#use-interactiveview-in-typed-handles)

## 생성 an Interactive Surface {#create-an-interactive-surface}

사용할 항목: `Dali::Ui::InteractiveView::New()` 경우 a 일반 interactive container should receive interaction 이벤트 directly. `Dali::Ui::InteractiveView`는 clickable를 통해 기본, 및 `SetClickable()` lets you enable 또는 suppress click generation 없이 changing the 객체 model.

```cpp
#include <dali-ui-foundation/public-api/interactive-view.h>

class PanelController
{
public:
  void Create()
  {
    Dali::Ui::InteractiveView panel =
      Dali::Ui::InteractiveView::New()
        .SetClickable(true)
        .SetPseudoDisabled(false)
        .SetKeyClickPolicy(Dali::Ui::KeyClickPolicy::ON_RELEASE);

    const bool canClick = panel.IsClickable();
    const bool disabled = panel.IsPseudoDisabled();

    (void)canClick;
    (void)disabled;
  }
};
```

`SetClickable(false)` 방지합니다 tap 및 key-click activation 동안 keeping the `Dali::Ui::InteractiveView` handle 및 its configured 시그널 intact. Combine it와(과) 함께 `SetPseudoDisabled()` 경우 the surface should look unavailable로 well로 stop click activation.

```cpp
void SetUnavailable(Dali::Ui::InteractiveView view, bool unavailable)
{
  view
    .SetClickable(!unavailable)
    .SetPseudoDisabled(unavailable);
}
```

## 처리 Clicks {#handle-clicks}

`ClickedSignal()` 반환합니다 a `Dali::Signal`와(과) 함께 콜백 shape `void(Dali::Ui::View, Dali::Ui::InputEvent)`. 해당 first argument는 the source `Dali::Ui::View`, 그래서 handlers can stay written와(과) the app-facing 뷰 model.

다음에 대해 concise setup, prefer `ConnectClickedSignal()`에서 `Dali::Ui::InteractiveView`. It 반환합니다 the 동일한 `Dali::Ui::InteractiveView`, 그래서 it fits fluent construction.

```cpp
class ClickController
{
public:
  void Create()
  {
    mButton =
      Dali::Ui::InteractiveView::New()
        .SetClickable(true)
        .ConnectClickedSignal(this, &ClickController::OnClicked);
  }

  void OnClicked(Dali::Ui::View view, Dali::Ui::InputEvent event)
  {
    ++mClickCount;

    (void)view;
    (void)event;
  }

private:
  Dali::Ui::InteractiveView mButton;
  int                       mClickCount{0};
};
```

You can also connect directly에 `ClickedSignal()` 경우 you want에 work와(과) 함께 the returned 시그널 객체.

```cpp
class DirectSignalController
{
public:
  void Create()
  {
    mButton = Dali::Ui::InteractiveView::New();

    mButton.ClickedSignal().Connect(
      this,
      &DirectSignalController::OnClicked);
  }

  void OnClicked(Dali::Ui::View view, Dali::Ui::InputEvent event)
  {
    mLastClicked = view;
    (void)event;
  }

private:
  Dali::Ui::InteractiveView mButton;
  Dali::Ui::View            mLastClicked;
};
```

## 제어 Keyboard Click Timing {#control-keyboard-click-timing}

`SetKeyClickPolicy()` 제어합니다 how D-Pad, remote, 또는 키보드 input becomes a click. 사용할 항목: `Dali::Ui::KeyClickPolicy::ON_RELEASE`에 emit clicked에서 release, `Dali::Ui::KeyClickPolicy::ON_PRESS`에 emit clicked에서 press, 또는 `Dali::Ui::KeyClickPolicy::DISABLED`에 prevent key input에서 producing click 이벤트.

```cpp
class KeyClickController
{
public:
  void UseReleaseActivation()
  {
    mActionView.SetKeyClickPolicy(Dali::Ui::KeyClickPolicy::ON_RELEASE);
  }

  void UseImmediateActivation()
  {
    mActionView.SetKeyClickPolicy(Dali::Ui::KeyClickPolicy::ON_PRESS);
  }

  void DisableKeyActivation()
  {
    mActionView.SetKeyClickPolicy(Dali::Ui::KeyClickPolicy::DISABLED);
  }

  bool IsImmediateActivation() const
  {
    return mActionView.GetKeyClickPolicy() == Dali::Ui::KeyClickPolicy::ON_PRESS;
  }

private:
  Dali::Ui::InteractiveView mActionView{Dali::Ui::InteractiveView::New()};
};
```

키보드 policy 및 포인터 clickability는 별도의 제어합니다. 뷰 can remain 포인터-clickable 동안 key-triggered clicks는 disabled.

```cpp
Dali::Ui::InteractiveView MakePointerOnlyAction()
{
  return Dali::Ui::InteractiveView::New()
    .SetClickable(true)
    .SetKeyClickPolicy(Dali::Ui::KeyClickPolicy::DISABLED);
}
```

## 눌림 및 의사 비활성 상태 추적 {#track-pressed-and-pseudo-disabled-state}

`PressedChangedSignal()` reports transitions로 및 out의 pressed state와(과) 함께 콜백 shape `void(Dali::Ui::View, bool, Dali::Ui::InputEvent)`. 사용할 항목: `IsPressed()` 경우 later code needs the 현재 상태.

```cpp
class PressController
{
public:
  void Create()
  {
    mSurface =
      Dali::Ui::InteractiveView::New()
        .ConnectPressedChangedSignal(this, &PressController::OnPressedChanged);
  }

  void OnPressedChanged(
    Dali::Ui::View       view,
    bool                 pressed,
    Dali::Ui::InputEvent event)
  {
    mPressed = pressed;

    const bool currentState = mSurface.IsPressed();

    (void)view;
    (void)event;
    (void)currentState;
  }

private:
  Dali::Ui::InteractiveView mSurface;
  bool                      mPressed{false};
};
```

`SetPseudoDisabled()` changes a 비주얼 pseudo-disabled 상태, 및 `PseudoDisabledChangedSignal()` reports that state와(과) 함께 콜백 shape `void(Dali::Ui::View, bool)`. pseudo-disabled view는 presented로 disabled but can still accept interaction; 경우 pseudo disabled는 set 동안 the view는 pressed, the pressed 상태는 cleared.

```cpp
class DisabledStateController
{
public:
  void Create()
  {
    mSurface = Dali::Ui::InteractiveView::New();

    mSurface.PseudoDisabledChangedSignal().Connect(
      this,
      &DisabledStateController::OnPseudoDisabledChanged);
  }

  void SetUnavailable(bool unavailable)
  {
    mSurface.SetPseudoDisabled(unavailable);
  }

  void OnPseudoDisabledChanged(Dali::Ui::View view, bool pseudoDisabled)
  {
    mUnavailable = pseudoDisabled;

    (void)view;
  }

private:
  Dali::Ui::InteractiveView mSurface;
  bool                      mUnavailable{false};
};
```

## 처리 Long Press {#handle-long-press}

`LongPressedSignal()` 사용합니다 콜백 shape `bool(Dali::Ui::View, Dali::Ui::InputEvent)`. Return `true` 경우 the long press consumes the interaction 및 should suppress the later click. Return `false` 경우 the click may still be emitted.

