## 연결 시그널 from a dali-ui Controller {#connect-signals-from-a-dali-ui-controller}

In a dali-ui 애플리케이션, keep 시그널 콜백에서 an 객체 that owns the UI 로직. Inherit에서 `Dali::ConnectionTracker` 경우 the controller should automatically disconnect its tracked 시그널 콜백 동안 destruction.

해당 common connection form is:

```cpp
signal.Connect(this, &Controller::OnSignal);
```

다음에 대해 member-함수 connections, the 콜백 signature must match the 시그널 signature.

```cpp
#include <dali-ui-foundation/public-api/view.h>
#include <dali/public-api/signals/connection-tracker.h>
#include <dali/public-api/signals/dali-signal.h>

class DetailsController : public Dali::ConnectionTracker
{
public:
  using ActivatedSignalType = Dali::Signal<void(Dali::Ui::View)>;

  void ConnectTo(ActivatedSignalType& activatedSignal)
  {
    activatedSignal.Connect(this, &DetailsController::OnActivated);
  }

private:
  void OnActivated(Dali::Ui::View view)
  {
    mLastActivatedView = view;
  }

  Dali::Ui::View mLastActivatedView;
};
```

`Dali::ConnectionTracker`는 the 일반적인 owner 위해 애플리케이션 콜백 때문에 it tracks connected slots 및 disconnects them 경우 the tracker goes away.

## 사용 Typed Signal Signatures {#use-typed-signal-signatures}

`Dali::Signal`는 specialized를 통해 함수 signature. Choose a signature that describes exactly what the 콜백 receives 및 반환합니다.

```cpp
#include <dali-ui-foundation/public-api/view.h>
