# 상태 이벤트 {#state-event}

`Dali::Ui::StateEvent` describes one `Dali::Ui::View` 상태 transition 및 gives 애플리케이션 code the previous 상태, 현재 상태, 및 input cause 경우 the transition originated에서 a concrete input 이벤트.

## 목차 {#table-of-contents}

- [Reacting에 뷰 상태 Transitions.](#reacting-to-view-state-transitions)
- [Detecting Added, Removed, 및 Changed 상태.](#detecting-added-removed-and-changed-states)
- [Reading the Previous 및 현재 상태 Snapshots.](#reading-the-previous-and-current-state-snapshots)
- [Using the Input 이벤트 Cause.](#using-the-input-event-cause)
- [Keeping 상태 Handlers Small.](#keeping-state-handlers-small)

## Reacting to 뷰 상태 Transitions {#reacting-to-view-state-transitions}

상태 이벤트는 delivered through `Dali::Ui::View::StateChangedSignal` 경우 a `Dali::Ui::View` changes 상태. In 애플리케이션 code, handle the 이벤트로 a short-lived 시그널 parameter 및 read the transition에서 the `Dali::Ui::StateEvent`.

```cpp
void OnStateChanged(Dali::Ui::View view, Dali::Ui::StateEvent event)
{
  if(event.Added(Dali::Ui::ViewState::FOCUSED))
  {
    // The view gained focus in this transition.
  }

  if(event.Removed(Dali::Ui::ViewState::PRESSED))
  {
    // The view is no longer pressed.
  }
}
```

`Dali::Ui::StateEvent`는 handle 타입. It can be copied 또는 assigned 경우 the 콜백 needs에 pass the 이벤트에 another local helper.

```cpp
void ForwardStateEvent(Dali::Ui::StateEvent event)
{
  Dali::Ui::StateEvent copiedEvent;
  copiedEvent = event;

  if(copiedEvent.Changed(Dali::Ui::ViewState::SELECTED))
  {
    // Selection state toggled.
  }
}
```

