# UI 테마 관리자 {#ui-theme-manager}

`Dali::Ui::UiThemeManager` lets a dali-ui 애플리케이션 read the 현재 테마 식별자 및 react 경우 the 테마 changes.

## 목차 {#table-of-contents}

- [Accessing the 테마 관리자.](#accessing-the-theme-manager)
- [Reading the 현재 테마.](#reading-the-current-theme)
- [Reacting에 테마 Changes.](#reacting-to-theme-changes)
- [Using 테마 State에서 a 뷰-Oriented App Layer.](#using-theme-state-from-a-view-oriented-app-layer)

## Accessing the 테마 관리자 {#accessing-the-theme-manager}

`Dali::Ui::UiThemeManager`는 handle-based singleton. 애플리케이션 code obtains the singleton handle와(과) 함께 `Dali::Ui::UiThemeManager::Get()` 및 유지합니다 the returned handle only로 long로 it는 useful.

```cpp
#include <dali-ui-foundation/public-api/ui-theme-manager.h>

class ThemeController
{
public:
  ThemeController()
  : mThemeManager(Dali::Ui::UiThemeManager::Get())
  {
  }

private:
  Dali::Ui::UiThemeManager mThemeManager;
};
```

다음 경우에는 your code receives a generic handle에서 infrastructure code, `Dali::Ui::UiThemeManager::DownCast()` can recover a `Dali::Ui::UiThemeManager` handle 경우 the 객체는 actually the 테마 관리자. 다음 경우에는 the handle는 not a 테마 관리자, the result는 uninitialized handle.

```cpp
#include <dali/public-api/object/base-handle.h>
#include <dali-ui-foundation/public-api/ui-theme-manager.h>

Dali::Ui::UiThemeManager AsThemeManager(Dali::BaseHandle handle)
{
  return Dali::Ui::UiThemeManager::DownCast(handle);
}
```

## Reading the Current 테마 {#reading-the-current-theme}

사용할 항목: `Dali::Ui::UiThemeManager::GetCurrentThemeId()` 경우 애플리케이션 로직 needs에 know which 테마는 현재. 해당 returned `Dali::String`는 the 테마 식별자; it can be empty 경우 no 테마는 active.

```cpp
#include <dali-ui-foundation/public-api/ui-theme-manager.h>

auto ReadThemeId()
{
  Dali::Ui::UiThemeManager themeManager = Dali::Ui::UiThemeManager::Get();
  return themeManager.GetCurrentThemeId();
}
```

다음에 대해 short-lived checks, it는 also valid에 query the singleton directly.

```cpp
#include <dali-ui-foundation/public-api/ui-theme-manager.h>

auto currentThemeId = Dali::Ui::UiThemeManager::Get().GetCurrentThemeId();
```

## Reacting to 테마 Changes {#reacting-to-theme-changes}

`Dali::Ui::UiThemeManager::ThemeChangedSignal()` 반환합니다 the 테마-change 시그널 owned를 통해 `Dali::Ui::UiThemeManager`. 해당 시그널 type는 `Dali::Signal<void()>`, 그래서 콜백 connected에 it take no arguments.

사용할 항목: `Dali::ConnectionTracker` 위해 receiver 객체 that own 시그널 connections.

```cpp
#include <dali/public-api/signals/connection-tracker.h>
#include <dali-ui-foundation/public-api/ui-theme-manager.h>

class ThemeObserver : public Dali::ConnectionTracker
{
public:
  ThemeObserver()
  {
    Dali::Ui::UiThemeManager themeManager = Dali::Ui::UiThemeManager::Get();
    themeManager.ThemeChangedSignal().Connect(this, &ThemeObserver::OnThemeChanged);
  }

private:
  void OnThemeChanged()
  {
    auto themeId = Dali::Ui::UiThemeManager::Get().GetCurrentThemeId();
    ApplyThemeId(themeId);
  }

  void ApplyThemeId(const decltype(Dali::Ui::UiThemeManager::Get().GetCurrentThemeId())& themeId)
  {
    mLastThemeId = themeId;
  }

  decltype(Dali::Ui::UiThemeManager::Get().GetCurrentThemeId()) mLastThemeId;
};
```

테마-change 콜백 should be small. Read the 현재 식별자와(과) 함께 `Dali::Ui::UiThemeManager::GetCurrentThemeId()`, 그런 다음 update the 애플리케이션 상태 that drives your dali-ui 뷰.

