# 뷰 상태 {#view-state}

`Dali::Ui::ViewState` 나타냅니다 one 또는 more 비주얼 및 interaction 상태의 a `Dali::Ui::View`로 a 간결한 값 that can be combined, queried, 및 compared.

## 목차 {#table-of-contents}

- [Representing 뷰 상태.](#representing-view-state)
- [Combining Built-In 상태.](#combining-built-in-states)
- [Testing 상태 위해 Styling Decisions.](#testing-state-for-styling-decisions)
- [Creating 사용자 지정 상태.](#creating-custom-states)
- [Detecting 상태 Transitions.](#detecting-state-transitions)
- [Debugging 상태 값.](#debugging-state-values)

## Representing 뷰 상태 {#representing-view-state}

사용할 항목: `Dali::Ui::ViewState` 경우 애플리케이션 code needs에 reason about the 상태의 a `Dali::Ui::View`. 기본-constructed `Dali::Ui::ViewState`는 the same로 `Dali::Ui::ViewState::NORMAL`, which has no 상태 bits set.

```cpp
#include <dali-ui-foundation/public-api/view-state.h>

using Dali::Ui::ViewState;

void CheckInitialState()
{
  ViewState state;

  if(state.IsNormal())
  {
    // The state is ViewState::NORMAL.
  }

  if(state == ViewState::NORMAL)
  {
    // Default construction and ViewState::NORMAL are equivalent.
  }

  if(!static_cast<bool>(state))
  {
    // ViewState::NORMAL has no active bits.
  }
}
```

`Dali::Ui::ViewState::operator bool`는 useful 경우 you only need에 know whether a 상태 값 포함합니다 any active bit. Prefer `IsNormal()` 경우 the code는 specifically checking 위해 `Dali::Ui::ViewState::NORMAL`.

## 내장 상태 결합 {#combining-built-in-states}

`Dali::Ui::ViewState`는 designed로 a bitmask 값. Built-in 상태 such로 `Dali::Ui::ViewState::FOCUSED`, `Dali::Ui::ViewState::PRESSED`, `Dali::Ui::ViewState::DISABLED`, `Dali::Ui::ViewState::PSEUDO_DISABLED`, 및 `Dali::Ui::ViewState::SELECTED` can be combined와(과) 함께 `operator+` 또는 `operator|`.

```cpp
#include <dali-ui-foundation/public-api/view-state.h>

using Dali::Ui::ViewState;

ViewState MakeInteractiveState(bool focused, bool pressed, bool selected)
{
  ViewState state = ViewState::NORMAL;

  if(focused)
  {
    state = state + ViewState::FOCUSED;
  }

  if(pressed)
  {
    state = state + ViewState::PRESSED;
  }

  if(selected)
  {
    state = state + ViewState::SELECTED;
  }

  return state;
}
```

Several common combinations는 already provided. 사용할 항목: `Dali::Ui::ViewState::SELECTED_PRESSED`, `Dali::Ui::ViewState::DISABLED_SELECTED`, 및 `Dali::Ui::ViewState::SELECTED_FOCUSED` 경우 those exact combinations match the 뷰 동작 you는 styling.

```cpp
#include <dali-ui-foundation/public-api/view-state.h>

using Dali::Ui::ViewState;

void UseCompositeStates()
{
  ViewState selectedPressed = ViewState::SELECTED_PRESSED;

  if(selectedPressed.Contains(ViewState::SELECTED) &&
     selectedPressed.Contains(ViewState::PRESSED))
  {
    // Apply selected-and-pressed styling.
  }

  ViewState selectedFocused = ViewState::SELECTED_FOCUSED;

  if(selectedFocused.Contains(ViewState::FOCUSED))
  {
    // Apply focused styling for a selected view.
  }
}
```

To remove a 상태 bit, use `Dali::Ui::ViewState::operator-`.

```cpp
#include <dali-ui-foundation/public-api/view-state.h>

using Dali::Ui::ViewState;

ViewState ClearPressed(ViewState state)
{
  return state - ViewState::PRESSED;
}

