## 생성 and Keep 뷰 Handles {#create-and-keep-view-handles}

사용할 항목: `Dali::Ui::View::New` 경우 you need an initialized general-purpose UI 객체. `Dali::Ui::View` handle refers에 the underlying 뷰 객체, 그래서 copying the handle 유지합니다 another reference에 the 동일한 뷰.

```cpp
#include <dali-ui-foundation/dali-ui-foundation.h>

using namespace Dali;
using namespace Dali::Ui;

View CreatePanel()
{
  View panel = View::New();
  return panel;
}
```

저장할 항목: `Dali::Ui::View` handles 위해 뷰 that you will inspect 또는 update later.

```cpp
class PageController
{
public:
  void Create()
  {
    mHeader = View::New();
    mContent = View::New();
  }

  Dali::String HeaderName() const
  {
    return mHeader.GetName();
  }

private:
  View mHeader;
  View mContent;
};
```

`Dali::Ui::View::GetName`, `Dali::Ui::View::GetColor`, `Dali::Ui::View::GetCurrentColor`, 및 `Dali::Ui::View::GetBackgroundColor`는 useful 경우 app code needs에 inspect 뷰 identity 또는 색상 상태.

```cpp
void ReadViewIdentity(View view)
{
  Dali::String name = view.GetName();
  UiColor color = view.GetColor();
  UiColor currentColor = view.GetCurrentColor();
  UiColor background = view.GetBackgroundColor();
}
```

