     7	# 웹 뷰 {#web-view}
     8	
     9	`Dali::Ui::WebView` displays web 콘텐츠 inside a dali-ui 애플리케이션 동안 staying에서 the `Dali::Ui::View` 객체 model.
    10	
    11	## 목차 {#table-of-contents}
    12	
    13	- [생성할 항목: 및 Configure a Web 뷰.](#create-and-configure-a-web-view)
    14	- [Load Pages 및 Local 콘텐츠.](#load-pages-and-local-content)
    15	- [Navigate 및 Track Page 상태.](#navigate-and-track-page-state)
    16	- [JavaScript 처리](#handle-javascript)
    17	- [Capture Page 콘텐츠.](#capture-page-content)
    18	- [Control Input, Scrolling, 및 Fullscreen.](#control-input-scrolling-and-fullscreen)
    19	- [Manage Rendering, Network, 및 Media 상태.](#manage-rendering-network-and-media-state)
    20	- [Web 뷰 Supporting 타입.](#web-view-supporting-types)
    21	
    22	## 생성 및 구성 a 웹 뷰 {#create-and-configure-a-web-view}
    23	
    24	생성할 항목: a web view와(과) 함께 `Dali::Ui::WebView::New`. `Dali::Ui::WebView`는 `Dali::Ui::View`, 그래서 애플리케이션 code can keep it에서 the dali-ui 뷰 tree 및 configure it through typed web-뷰 setters 대신 원시 속성 calls.
    25	
    26	```cpp
    27	Dali::Ui::WebView webView = Dali::Ui::WebView::New();
    28	
    29	webView
    30	  .SetUserAgent(Dali::String("MyDaliUiApp/1.0"))
    31	  .SetMouseEventsEnabled(true)
    32	  .SetKeyEventsEnabled(true)
    33	  .SetVideoHoleEnabled(true)
    34	  .SetDocumentBackgroundColor(Dali::Vector4(1.0f, 1.0f, 1.0f, 1.0f))
    35	  .SetPageZoomFactor(1.0f)
    36	  .SetTextZoomFactor(1.0f)
    37	  .SetTilesClearedWhenHidden(true)
    38	  .SetTileCoverAreaMultiplier(2.0f)
    39	  .SetCursorEnabledByClient(true);
    40	```
    41	
    42	사용할 항목: the matching getters 경우 UI 상태 depends에서 the 현재 구성.
    43	
    44	```cpp
    45	const bool mouseEnabled = webView.GetMouseEventsEnabled();
    46	const bool keyEnabled   = webView.GetKeyEventsEnabled();
    47	const bool videoHole    = webView.GetVideoHoleEnabled();
    48	
    49	const float pageZoom = webView.GetPageZoomFactor();
    50	const float textZoom = webView.GetTextZoomFactor();
    51	const float scale    = webView.GetScaleFactor();
    52	
    53	Dali::String userAgent = webView.GetUserAgent();
    54	```
    55	
    56	다음 경우에는 a handle는 stored로 a base `Dali::Ui::View`, recover the web-뷰 API와(과) 함께 `Dali::Ui::WebView::DownCast`.
    57	
    58	```cpp
    59	Dali::Ui::View view = webView;
    60	
    61	Dali::Ui::WebView castWebView = Dali::Ui::WebView::DownCast(view);
    62	if(castWebView)
    63	{
    64	  castWebView.Reload();
    65	}
    66	```
    67	
    68	## 페이지와 로컬 콘텐츠 로드 {#load-pages-and-local-content}
    69	
    70	사용할 항목: `Dali::Ui::WebView::LoadUrl` 위해 remote URLs 또는 파일 URLs. 사용할 항목: `Dali::Ui::WebView::LoadHtmlString` 경우 the 애플리케이션 already has an HTML string.
    71	
    72	```cpp
    73	Dali::Ui::WebView webView = Dali::Ui::WebView::New();
    74	
    75	webView.LoadUrl(Dali::String("https://www.example.com"));
    76	```
    77	
    78	```cpp
    79	Dali::Ui::WebView webView = Dali::Ui::WebView::New();
    80	
    81	webView.LoadHtmlString(Dali::String(
    82	  "<html>"
    83	  "<head><title>Offline</title></head>"
    84	  "<body>"
    85	  "<h1>Offline content</h1>"
    86	  "<p>This page was supplied by the application.</p>"
    87	  "</body>"
    88	  "</html>"));
    89	```
    90	
    91	다음에 대해 byte buffers, `Dali::Ui::WebView::LoadContents` 받습니다 the 콘텐츠 포인터, byte 크기, MIME 타입, encoding, 및 base URI. `Dali::Ui::WebView::LoadHtmlStringOverrideCurrentEntry` 로드합니다 an HTML document 동안 replacing the 현재 history entry.
    92	
    93	```cpp
    94	const char html[] =
    95	  "<html><body><h1>Embedded content</h1></body></html>";
    96	
    97	const bool loaded = webView.LoadContents(
    98	  reinterpret_cast<const int8_t*>(html),
    99	  static_cast<uint32_t>(sizeof(html) - 1u),
   100	  Dali::String("text/html"),
   101	  Dali::String("UTF-8"),
   102	  Dali::String("https://app.local/"));
   103	
   104	if(!loaded)
   105	{
   106	  webView.LoadHtmlString(Dali::String("<html><body>Fallback</body></html>"));
   107	}
   108	```
   109	
   110	```cpp
   111	const bool replaced = webView.LoadHtmlStringOverrideCurrentEntry(
   112	  Dali::String("<html><body><h1>Replacement</h1></body></html>"),
   113	  Dali::String("https://app.local/"),
   114	  Dali::String("https://app.local/unreachable"));
   115	
   116	if(replaced)
   117	{
   118	  webView.ClearHistory();
   119	}
   120	```
   121	
   122	사용할 항목: 사용자 지정 headers 전에 loading the request that needs them.
   123	
   124	```cpp
   125	if(webView.AddCustomHeader(Dali::String("X-App-Mode"), Dali::String("embedded")))
   126	{
   127	  webView.LoadUrl(Dali::String("https://www.example.com/dashboard"));
   128	  webView.RemoveCustomHeader(Dali::String("X-App-Mode"));
   129	}
   130	```
   131	
   132	## 페이지 이동 및 상태 추적 {#navigate-and-track-page-state}
   133	
   134	`Dali::Ui::WebView` owns page navigation commands such로 `Dali::Ui::WebView::GoBack`, `Dali::Ui::WebView::GoForward`, `Dali::Ui::WebView::Reload`, `Dali::Ui::WebView::ReloadWithoutCache`, `Dali::Ui::WebView::StopLoading`, 및 `Dali::Ui::WebView::ClearHistory`.
   135	
   136	```cpp
   137	if(webView.CanGoBack())
   138	{
   139	  webView.GoBack();
   140	}
   141	else
   142	{
   143	  webView.LoadUrl(Dali::String("https://www.example.com"));
   144	}
   145	
   146	if(webView.CanGoForward())
   147	{
   148	  webView.GoForward();
   149	}
   150	
   151	webView.Reload();
   152	
   153	const bool reloadStarted = webView.ReloadWithoutCache();
   154	if(!reloadStarted)
   155	{
   156	  webView.StopLoading();
   157	}
   158	```
   159	
   160	연결할 항목:에 web-뷰 시그널에 keep 애플리케이션 UI synchronized와(과) 함께 the page. Page-load 및 URL-change 시그널 pass the `Dali::Ui::WebView` 및 the URL. `Dali::Ui::WebView::FrameRenderedSignal` passes the `Dali::Ui::WebView`.
   161	
   162	```cpp
   163	class BrowserController : public Dali::ConnectionTracker
   164	{
   165	public:
   166	  void Attach(Dali::Ui::WebView webView)
   167	  {
   168	    mWebView = webView;
   169	
   170	    mWebView.PageLoadStartedSignal().Connect(
   171	      this,
   172	      &BrowserController::OnPageLoadStarted);
   173	
   174	    mWebView.PageLoadFinishedSignal().Connect(
   175	      this,
   176	      &BrowserController::OnPageLoadFinished);
   177	
   178	    mWebView.UrlChangedSignal().Connect(
   179	      this,
   180	      &BrowserController::OnUrlChanged);
   181	
   182	    mWebView.FrameRenderedSignal().Connect(
   183	      this,
   184	      &BrowserController::OnFrameRendered);
   185	  }
   186	
   187	private:
   188	  void OnPageLoadStarted(Dali::Ui::WebView view, const Dali::String& url)
   189	  {
   190	    const float progress = view.GetLoadProgressPercentage();
   191	  }
   192	
   193	  void OnPageLoadFinished(Dali::Ui::WebView view, const Dali::String& url)
   194	  {
   195	    Dali::String title = view.GetTitle();
   196	    Dali::String currentUrl = view.GetUrl();
   197	  }
   198	
   199	  void OnUrlChanged(Dali::Ui::WebView view, const Dali::String& url)
   200	  {
   201	    Dali::String currentUrl = url;
   202	  }
   203	
   204	  void OnFrameRendered(Dali::Ui::WebView view)
   205	  {
   206	    Dali::Vector2 contentSize = view.GetContentSize();
   207	  }
   208	
   209	  Dali::Ui::WebView mWebView;
   210	};
   211	```
   212	
   213	## JavaScript 처리 {#handle-javascript}
   214	
   215	사용할 항목: `Dali::Ui::WebView::EvaluateJavaScript` 위해 애플리케이션-driven script execution. 해당 콜백 overload 반환합니다 the script 결과로 a `Dali::String`.
   216	
   217	```cpp
   218	class ScriptBridge : public Dali::ConnectionTracker
   219	{
   220	public:
   221	  void Attach(Dali::Ui::WebView webView)
   222	  {
   223	    mWebView = webView;
   224	  }
   225	
   226	  void ReadTitle()
   227	  {
   228	    mWebView.EvaluateJavaScript(
   229	      Dali::String("document.title"),
   230	      Dali::Ui::WebView::JavaScriptCallback::New(
   231	        this,
   232	        &ScriptBridge::OnJavaScriptResult));
   233	  }
   234	
   235	private:
   236	  void OnJavaScriptResult(const Dali::String& result)
   237	  {
   238	    mLastResult = result;
   239	  }
   240	
   241	  Dali::Ui::WebView mWebView;
   242	  Dali::String      mLastResult;
   243	};
   244	```
   245	
   246	`Dali::Ui::WebView::AddJavaScriptMessageHandler` 등록합니다 an exposed 객체 name that page scripts can use에 send messages에 the 애플리케이션-side 콜백.
   247	
   248	```cpp
   249	class MessageBridge : public Dali::ConnectionTracker
   250	{
   251	public:
   252	  void Attach(Dali::Ui::WebView webView)
   253	  {
   254	    mWebView = webView;
   255	
   256	    mWebView.AddJavaScriptMessageHandler(
   257	      Dali::String("appBridge"),
   258	      Dali::Ui::WebView::JavaScriptCallback::New(
   259	        this,
   260	        &MessageBridge::OnMessageFromPage));
   261	  }
   262	
   263	private:
   264	  void OnMessageFromPage(const Dali::String& message)
   265	  {
   266	    mLastMessage = message;
   267	  }
   268	
   269	  Dali::Ui::WebView mWebView;
   270	  Dali::String      mLastMessage;
   271	};
   272	```
   273	
   274	JavaScript dialogs는 handled를 통해 registering 콜백 및 later replying through the matching reply 메서드. `Dali::Ui::WebView::RegisterJavaScriptAlertCallback` pairs와(과) 함께 `Dali::Ui::WebView::JavaScriptAlertReply`; `Dali::Ui::WebView::RegisterJavaScriptConfirmCallback` pairs와(과) 함께 `Dali::Ui::WebView::JavaScriptConfirmReply`; `Dali::Ui::WebView::RegisterJavaScriptPromptCallback` pairs와(과) 함께 `Dali::Ui::WebView::JavaScriptPromptReply`.
   275	
   276	```cpp
   277	class DialogBridge : public Dali::ConnectionTracker
   278	{
   279	public:
   280	  void Attach(Dali::Ui::WebView webView)
   281	  {
   282	    mWebView = webView;
   283	
   284	    mWebView.RegisterJavaScriptAlertCallback(
   285	      Dali::Ui::WebView::JavaScriptAlertCallback::New(
   286	        this,
   287	        &DialogBridge::OnAlert));
   288	
   289	    mWebView.RegisterJavaScriptConfirmCallback(
   290	      Dali::Ui::WebView::JavaScriptConfirmCallback::New(
   291	        this,
   292	        &DialogBridge::OnConfirm));
   293	
   294	    mWebView.RegisterJavaScriptPromptCallback(
   295	      Dali::Ui::WebView::JavaScriptPromptCallback::New(
   296	        this,
   297	        &DialogBridge::OnPrompt));
   298	  }
   299	
   300	private:
   301	  bool OnAlert(const Dali::String& message)
   302	  {
   303	    mWebView.JavaScriptAlertReply();
   304	    return true;
   305	  }
   306	
   307	  bool OnConfirm(const Dali::String& message)
   308	  {
   309	    mWebView.JavaScriptConfirmReply(true);
   310	    return true;
   311	  }
   312	
   313	  bool OnPrompt(const Dali::String& message, const Dali::String& defaultValue)
   314	  {
   315	    mWebView.JavaScriptPromptReply(defaultValue);
   316	    return true;
   317	  }
   318	
   319	  Dali::Ui::WebView mWebView;
   320	};
   321	```
   322	
   323	## 페이지 콘텐츠 캡처 {#capture-page-content}
   324	
   325	`Dali::Ui::WebView::GetScreenshot` 반환합니다 a `Dali::Ui::ImageView` 위해 the requested rectangle 및 스케일. 사용할 항목: `Dali::Ui::WebView::GetScreenshotAsynchronously` 경우 capture work should complete through a 콜백.
   326	
   327	```cpp
   328	Dali::BoundsInteger area(0, 0, 320, 240);
   329	
   330	Dali::Ui::ImageView screenshot = webView.GetScreenshot(area, 1.0f);
   331	```
   332	
   333	```cpp
   334	class CaptureController : public Dali::ConnectionTracker
   335	{
   336	public:
   337	  void Attach(Dali::Ui::WebView webView)
   338	  {
   339	    mWebView = webView;
   340	  }
   341	
   342	  void Capture()
   343	  {
   344	    Dali::BoundsInteger area(0, 0, 320, 240);
   345	
   346	    const bool started = mWebView.GetScreenshotAsynchronously(
   347	      area,
   348	      1.0f,
   349	      Dali::Ui::WebView::ScreenshotCapturedCallback::New(
   350	        this,
   351	        &CaptureController::OnScreenshotCaptured));
   352	
   353	    if(!started)
   354	    {
   355	      mFallbackImage = mWebView.GetScreenshot(area, 1.0f);
   356	    }
   357	  }
   358	
   359	private:
   360	  void OnScreenshotCaptured(Dali::Ui::ImageView screenshot)
   361	  {
   362	    mLastScreenshot = screenshot;
   363	  }
   364	
   365	  Dali::Ui::WebView  mWebView;
   366	  Dali::Ui::ImageView mLastScreenshot;
   367	  Dali::Ui::ImageView mFallbackImage;
   368	};
   369	```
   370	
   371	사용할 항목: the page information APIs에 update surrounding app chrome 없이 inspecting the 원시 page yourself.
   372	
   373	```cpp
   374	Dali::String title        = webView.GetTitle();
   375	Dali::String url          = webView.GetUrl();
   376	Dali::String selectedText = webView.GetSelectedText();
   377	
   378	Dali::Vector2 scrollPosition = webView.GetScrollPosition();
   379	Dali::Vector2 scrollSize     = webView.GetScrollSize();
   380	Dali::Vector2 contentSize    = webView.GetContentSize();
   381	
   382	Dali::Ui::ImageView favicon = webView.GetFavicon();
   383	```
   384	
   385	일반 텍스트 extraction는 asynchronous.
   386	
   387	```cpp
   388	class TextExtractor : public Dali::ConnectionTracker
   389	{
   390	public:
   391	  void Attach(Dali::Ui::WebView webView)
   392	  {
   393	    mWebView = webView;
   394	  }
   395	
   396	  void RequestText()
   397	  {
   398	    mWebView.GetPlainTextAsynchronously(
   399	      Dali::Ui::WebView::PlainTextCallback::New(
   400	        this,
   401	        &TextExtractor::OnPlainText));
   402	  }
   403	
   404	private:
   405	  void OnPlainText(const Dali::String& text)
   406	  {
   407	    mText = text;
   408	  }
   409	
   410	  Dali::Ui::WebView mWebView;
   411	  Dali::String      mText;
   412	};
   413	```
   414	
   415	## 입력, 스크롤 및 전체 화면 제어 {#control-input-scrolling-and-fullscreen}
   416	
   417	`Dali::Ui::WebView` 노출합니다 input enablement through typed setters 및 getters.
   418	
   419	```cpp
   420	webView
   421	  .SetMouseEventsEnabled(true)
   422	  .SetKeyEventsEnabled(true)
   423	  .SetCursorEnabledByClient(true);
   424	
   425	if(webView.GetMouseEventsEnabled())
   426	{
   427	  webView.FeedMouseWheel(true, 1, 160, 120);
   428	}
   429	```
   430	
   431	사용할 항목: `Dali::Ui::WebView::ScrollBy` 위해 ordinary scroll deltas 및 `Dali::Ui::WebView::ScrollEdgeBy` 경우 edge-aware scrolling는 needed.
   432	
   433	```cpp
   434	webView.ScrollBy(0, 120);
   435	
   436	const bool edgeScrolled = webView.ScrollEdgeBy(0, 80);
   437	if(!edgeScrolled)
   438	{
   439	  Dali::Vector2 position = webView.GetScrollPosition();
   440	}
   441	```
   442	
   443	Scroll 및 fullscreen 이벤트는 delivered through web-뷰 시그널. `Dali::Ui::WebView::OverScrolledSignal` 사용합니다 `Dali::Ui::WebViewOverScrolled`, 및 `Dali::Ui::WebView::ScrollEdgeReachedSignal` 사용합니다 `Dali::Ui::WebViewScrollEdge`.
   444	
   445	```cpp
   446	class WebInteractionController : public Dali::ConnectionTracker
   447	{
   448	public:
   449	  void Attach(Dali::Ui::WebView webView)
   450	  {
   451	    mWebView = webView;
   452	
   453	    mWebView.OverScrolledSignal().Connect(
   454	      this,
   455	      &WebInteractionController::OnOverScrolled);
   456	
   457	    mWebView.ScrollEdgeReachedSignal().Connect(
   458	      this,
   459	      &WebInteractionController::OnScrollEdgeReached);
   460	
   461	    mWebView.FullscreenEnteredSignal().Connect(
   462	      this,
   463	      &WebInteractionController::OnFullscreenEntered);
   464	
   465	    mWebView.FullscreenExitedSignal().Connect(
   466	      this,
   467	      &WebInteractionController::OnFullscreenExited);
   468	  }
   469	
   470	private:
   471	  void OnOverScrolled(Dali::Ui::WebView view, Dali::Ui::WebViewOverScrolled direction)
   472	  {
   473	    if(direction == Dali::Ui::WebViewOverScrolled::BOTTOM)
   474	    {
   475	      view.ScrollBy(0, -40);
   476	    }
   477	  }
   478	
   479	  void OnScrollEdgeReached(Dali::Ui::WebView view, Dali::Ui::WebViewScrollEdge edge)
   480	  {
   481	    if(edge == Dali::Ui::WebViewScrollEdge::LEFT && view.CanGoBack())
   482	    {
   483	      view.GoBack();
   484	    }
   485	  }
   486	
   487	  void OnFullscreenEntered(Dali::Ui::WebView view)
   488	  {
   489	    mFullscreen = true;
   490	  }
   491	
   492	  void OnFullscreenExited(Dali::Ui::WebView view)
   493	  {
   494	    mFullscreen = false;
   495	  }
   496	
   497	  Dali::Ui::WebView mWebView;
   498	  bool              mFullscreen{false};
   499	};
   500	```
   501	
   502	Exit fullscreen에서 the 애플리케이션와(과) 함께 `Dali::Ui::WebView::ExitFullscreen`.
   503	
   504	```cpp
   505	webView.ExitFullscreen();
   506	```
   507	
   508	## 렌더링, 네트워크 및 미디어 상태 관리 {#manage-rendering-network-and-media-state}
   509	
   510	사용할 항목: `Dali::Ui::WebView::Suspend` 및 `Dali::Ui::WebView::Resume` 위해 the web 뷰 lifecycle, 및 `Dali::Ui::WebView::SuspendNetworkLoading` 또는 `Dali::Ui::WebView::ResumeNetworkLoading` 경우 only network activity should be paused 또는 resumed.
   511	
   512	```cpp
   513	void OnAppPaused(Dali::Ui::WebView webView)
   514	{
   515	  webView.SuspendNetworkLoading();
   516	  webView.Suspend();
   517	}
   518	
   519	void OnAppResumed(Dali::Ui::WebView webView)
   520	{
   521	  webView.Resume();
   522	  webView.ResumeNetworkLoading();
   523	}
   524	```
   525	
   526	Tile 및 스케일 제어합니다는 owned를 통해 `Dali::Ui::WebView`. They는 useful 경우 the surrounding app changes page presentation 또는 visibility.
   527	
   528	```cpp
   529	webView
   530	  .SetTilesClearedWhenHidden(true)
   531	  .SetTileCoverAreaMultiplier(2.0f);
   532	
   533	webView.SetScaleFactor(1.25f, Dali::Vector2(120.0f, 160.0f));
   534	
   535	const float scale = webView.GetScaleFactor();
   536	
   537	webView.ClearAllTilesResources();
   538	```
   539	
   540	Video 상태는 checked asynchronously와(과) 함께 `Dali::Ui::WebView::CheckVideoPlayingAsynchronously`.
   541	
   542	```cpp
   543	class MediaStateController : public Dali::ConnectionTracker
   544	{
   545	public:
   546	  void Attach(Dali::Ui::WebView webView)
   547	  {
   548	    mWebView = webView;
   549	    mWebView.SetVideoHoleEnabled(true);
   550	  }
   551	
   552	  void RefreshVideoState()
   553	  {
   554	    mWebView.CheckVideoPlayingAsynchronously(
   555	      Dali::Ui::WebView::VideoPlayingCallback::New(
   556	        this,
   557	        &MediaStateController::OnVideoPlaying));
   558	  }
   559	
   560	private:
   561	  void OnVideoPlaying(bool playing)
   562	  {
   563	    mVideoPlaying = playing;
   564	  }
   565	
   566	  Dali::Ui::WebView mWebView;
   567	  bool              mVideoPlaying{false};
   568	};
   569	```
   570	
   571	Handle geolocation permission requests 및 web 프로세스 crashes through the owning 시그널.
   572	
   573	```cpp
   574	class PermissionAndRecoveryController : public Dali::ConnectionTracker
   575	{
   576	public:
   577	  void Attach(Dali::Ui::WebView webView)
   578	  {
   579	    mWebView = webView;
   580	
   581	    mWebView.GeolocationPermissionSignal().Connect(
   582	      this,
   583	      &PermissionAndRecoveryController::OnGeolocationPermission);
   584	
   585	    mWebView.WebProcessCrashedSignal().Connect(
   586	      this,
   587	      &PermissionAndRecoveryController::OnWebProcessCrashed);
   588	  }
   589	
   590	private:
   591	  bool OnGeolocationPermission(
   592	    Dali::Ui::WebView view,
   593	    const Dali::String& host,
   594	    const Dali::String& protocol)
   595	  {
   596	    return protocol == Dali::String("https");
   597	  }
   598	
   599	  void OnWebProcessCrashed(Dali::Ui::WebView view)
   600	  {
   601	    view.ReloadWithoutCache();
   602	  }
   603	
   604	  Dali::Ui::WebView mWebView;
   605	};
   606	```
